# .mgrepignore — exclude from mgrep index to free token budget
# Created: 2026-04-18 (Phase 0.26 S5)
#
# Purpose: reduce mgrep index size by excluding paths that don't benefit
# from semantic search. Each line is a gitignore-style pattern.

# tmp files (watcher artifacts, editor swap files, etc.)
*.tmp
*.tmp.*
tmp/
.tmp/

# Visual schedule migrations (large auto-generated migration SQL,
# not useful for cross-feature semantic search)
supabase/migrations/*visual_schedule*.sql

# OPTIONAL: exclude public assets from index (uncomment if needed).
# Leaving indexed by default to preserve search against public HTML/images.
# public/**
